    <string name="help_text">How to use:\n1. On your TV box, open Settings → Bluetooth (or Remotes &amp; accessories) and start pairing.\n2. Tap Pair… above and pair your phone with the TV box from the phone’s Bluetooth settings.\n3. Back in this app, tap Refresh, pick the TV box, then Connect.\n4. Open any app on the TV (browser, Tor, search…), focus a text field, and type or paste here.\nThe TV sees your phone as a real hardware keyboard, so it works inside every app.</string>
